    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>First of the periods in Andean prehistory dating from before the introduction of ceramic artifacts into the archaeological record, generally dating before 9500 BCE to 1800 BCE. Pre-Ceramic may be broken into six smaller periods, labeled I through VI.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
